import { Box, Flex } from "@chakra-ui/react"


export const Forgot = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Flex w={"full"} h={"648px"} bgGradient="linear(#FFC900, #FFEA61)" justifyContent={"center"}>
                <Box mt={"75px"} bg={"white"} w={"600px"} h={"300px"} border={"2px solid"} borderColor={"black"} borderRadius={"10px"} boxShadow={"0px 0px 10px black"} justifyContent={"center"}>
                    <Flex justifyContent={"center"}>
                        <Heading mt={"50px"} color={"#D5AD18"} fontSize={"60px"} fontFamily={"Times New Roman"}>LOGIN</Heading>
                    </Flex>
                </Box>
            </Flex>
        </>
    )
}
